<li><a href="/scp-600-co">SCP-600-CO</a> (&quot;A Super Cool Friend Watched My Plant&quot;) - OK, so I've cleaned your house, nourished your pets and, of course, your plant is still healthy and all that. A pleasure to help. Water provided by Roget.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-5985">SCP-5985</a> (&quot;Waters of Wisdom&quot;) - Since humanity had began to exist, everything wants to found their own secret of the infinite wisdom. Written by Jakiboy Omega.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-4576">SCP-4576</a> (&quot;The Best-Laid Plans&quot;) - Well, it was supposed to be that. Plants cultivated by barredowl.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-5070">SCP-5070</a> (&quot;Goodbye, Mr. Blue Sky&quot;) - &quot;<em>Di-di-di-did you ever wonder / Why we had to run for shelter / When the promise of a brave new world / When you could have other friends than a cube.</em>&quot; Written by DrUnoriginal.</li>
