<li><a href="/scp-720">SCP-720</a> (&quot;Panopticon&quot;) - There were video games with little kids as protagonists before <em>Undertale</em> and <em>Earthbound</em>. Yeah, the one I talk about wasn't famous, but still. Written by Popsioak.</li>
