<li><a href="/scp-5027">SCP-5027</a> (&quot;Schrödinger's Man&quot;) - Hey, after all these years, it was obvious&#8230; what do you mean, it's not the cat? Written by deathbygin.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-5352">SCP-5352</a> (&quot;Absence&quot;) - No, there's no blurb here. It's supposed to have an absence of a blurb. Scroll down, there's nothing to watch. Written by Ihp.</li>
